                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/17" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0065</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10510 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">走过危机：2009，中联重科在迪拜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Go Across the Crisis: Zoomlion in Dubai</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蓝茵茵，梁向东等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长沙理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中联重科</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">主权债务危机；金融危机；危机预警；中联重科；迪拜；2011百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sovereign Debt Crisis; Financial Crisis; Early-warning of Crisis; Zoomlion; Dubai</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">迪拜酋长国由于其独特的经济发展模式和区位优势，吸引了全球优秀的工程机械企业在此投资、经营，中联重科即是其中之一。2008年起由美国引发全球金融危机、尤其是2009年底迪拜爆发主权债务危机后，当地的工程机械市场遭受巨大冲击，中联重科等企业在迪拜的经营等活动严重受挫。本案例首先叙述中联重科在迪拜市场的发展历程，然后描述了在双重危机的背景下，公司海外一线员工的切身感受和思考，以及公司管理层面对危机的决策过程，最后介绍了中联重科对危机后迪拜市场的发展预测和对整个危机预警及管理过程的反思。本案例所涉及的情况对于意图或正在进行海外市场开拓、跨国经营管理的中国企业有一定的借鉴作用。当外部环境出现危机、行业市场风险遽增时，跨国企业的管理者、员工是否能正确判断和及时应对，企业的组织结构、战略是否能适应环境的剧变和进行相应调整，将是企业在海外市场能否生存并持续发展的关键。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Because of Dubai’s unique pattern of the economy development and its advantage of the location, it attracts enterprises in engineering machine industry all over the world such as Zoomlion. However, the local market was struck hard by the world financial crisis which firstly occurred in U.S.A., and especially the sovereign debt crisis which broke out in Dubai itself. The case described the history of Zoomlion’s work in Dubai, and then pictured how their staffs abroad feel and what they have done during the double crisis, as well as the decision-making process of the management class. This case also introduced Zoomlion’s thought of the post-crisis market and its self-examination to the early-warning and the management of the crisis. Lessons learned from this case can be used for reference for the Chinese enterprises on how to predict and control the risk of outer crisis during the multi-national management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《跨国管理》、《国际商务》、《国际营销》、《企业战略管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际市场、海外市场的选择与进入模式、企业与当地政府的关系、全球经济局势、主权风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
